## AI-PLC Agent Instructions

### AIPO Workflow

| Phase | Skill | Purpose |
|-------|-------|---------|
| Collection | `ai-plc/01-collection` | Goal設定・Context収集・Execution Context確立 |
| Inception | `ai-plc/02-inception` | Goal分解・Backlog生成 |
